    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Try using <a href=\"http://commons.apache.org/io/apidocs/org/apache/commons/io/FileUtils.html#write\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>FileUtils.write</code></a> from Apache Commons.</p>\n\n<p>You should be able to do something like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>File f = new File(\"output.txt\"); \nFileUtils.writeStringToFile(f, document.outerHtml(), \"UTF-8\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>This will create the file if it does not exist.</p>\n"
